{
  "info": {
    "name": "Camel Spotify API",
    "description": "Colección para probar la integración de Spotify API con Apache Camel + Spring Boot.\n\n**Cómo usar:**\n1. Ejecutá 'Obtener Token' en la carpeta Auth\n2. El token se guarda automáticamente en la variable {{jwt_token}}\n3. Todos los requests de Spotify ya lo usan automáticamente",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "https://merry-spirit-production-08fd.up.railway.app",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Cambiá a http://localhost:8080 para probar local"
    },
    {
      "key": "jwt_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Se llena automáticamente al ejecutar POST /auth/token"
    },
    {
      "key": "client_id",
      "value": "camel-client",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "client_secret",
      "value": "camel-secret-2024",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Obtener Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('jwt_token', jsonData.token);",
                  "    console.log('Token guardado correctamente');",
                  "    pm.test('Token recibido', function() { pm.expect(jsonData.token).to.not.be.empty; });",
                  "    pm.test('Expira en 3600s', function() { pm.expect(jsonData.expiresIn).to.eql(3600); });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"clientId\": \"{{client_id}}\",\n  \"clientSecret\": \"{{client_secret}}\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/token",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "token"]
            },
            "description": "Obtiene un JWT válido por 1 hora.\n\n**El token se guarda automáticamente** en la variable `{{jwt_token}}` y todos los requests de búsqueda lo usan sin que tengas que hacer nada."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Obtener Token - Credenciales Incorrectas",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"clientId\": \"cliente-invalido\",\n  \"clientSecret\": \"secret-invalido\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/token",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "token"]
            },
            "description": "Debe devolver **401 Unauthorized**. Útil para verificar que el sistema rechaza credenciales inválidas."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Tracks",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Buscar tracks - Radiohead",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/spotify/search?q=radiohead&type=track",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "spotify", "search"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "q", "value": "radiohead" },
                { "key": "type", "value": "track" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
